This script downloads the source code from Git.

The generated package will be installed in /usr.

Packages built from Git are not recognized as separate versions by Slackware's
package tools. To reinstall or upgrade a Git build, use:

upgradepkg --install-new --reinstall /tmp/wine-tkg...

Remember that if an installer creates a desktop shortcut, the generated
.desktop file will contain the path to the Wine binary that was used
during installation.

Wine stores Windows application launchers here:

~/.local/share/applications/wine/Programs/

TODO: More build options will be added.

Build options
-------------

Example:

PLAIN_VERSION=wine-11.9 STAGING_VERSION=v11.9 ./wine-tkg.SlackBuild

PLAIN_VERSION           Default=
STAGING_VERSION         Default=

USE_STAGING             Default=YES
USE_GE_PATCHES          Default=YES
PROTONIFY               Default=NO
LOCAL_PRESET_PROMPT     Default=NO
ALLOW_SERVER_RT_PRIO    Default=YES
WAYLAND                 Default=NO

NTSYNC                  Default=NO
FASTSYNC                Default=NO
ESYNC                   Default=YES
FSYNC                   Default=YES

Dependencies
------------

Dependencies may change over time, so check what your applications
require. Some optional dependencies may be missing while the build
still completes successfully.

For Slackware 15, install AlienBOB's multilib packages and MinGW.

Without MinGW, Wine cannot build DLLs correctly, and some Windows
applications may not work. Reboot after installing MinGW.

https://slackbuilds.org/repository/15.0/system/schedtool/
http://www.slackware.com/~alien/slackbuilds/MinGW-w64/pkg64/15.0/

Wayland 32-bit development files were not found.
The Wayland driver will not be built.
This appears to be a Slackware 15 limitation.

Optional dependencies
---------------------

fontforge

Builds the tahoma, tahomabd, and marlett fonts.

http://www.slackware.com/~alien/slackbuilds/fontforge/pkg64/15.0/
or
https://slackbuilds.org/repository/15.0/graphics/fontforge/

webcore-fonts

Provides Microsoft's core web fonts and Windows Vista fonts.

https://slackbuilds.org/repository/15.0/system/webcore-fonts/

The following missing components are common and usually not needed:

OSS sound system found, but it is too old (OSSv4 required). OSS support will be disabled.
libcapi20 not found. Smart card support will be disabled.
pcsc-lite 64-bit development files not found. ISDN support will be disabled.
